WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.980
Betty, what are our lessons on Monday?

00:04.980 --> 00:12.200
We have Chinese at 8 o'clock and science at 5 to 9.

00:12.200 --> 00:16.440
At 20 past 10 we have IT.

00:16.440 --> 00:18.080
Then we have Maths.

00:18.080 --> 00:21.480
Do you like Maths Tony?

00:21.480 --> 00:26.720
Yes, I do, but it's difficult.

00:26.720 --> 00:34.520
I like the lessons on Monday afternoon, English and Art.

00:34.520 --> 00:38.040
What lessons do we have on Friday?

00:38.040 --> 00:45.720
We have English, Chinese, PE and geography.

00:45.720 --> 00:49.920
And in the afternoon do we have Maths?

00:49.920 --> 00:52.080
No, we don't.

00:52.080 --> 00:57.760
We have Art and History, but we don't have Maths.

00:57.760 --> 01:02.280
I love History and I'm good at it.

01:02.280 --> 01:07.560
It's my favorite subject because it's very interesting.

01:07.560 --> 01:11.280
My favorite subject is Chinese.

01:11.280 --> 01:13.920
I can talk with my Chinese friends.

